{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_2784a0cd0ffegdT3ebJH7Cju7R","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d87b60528001ED2R4yEIlGBbIN","parts":[{"id":"prt_d87b60c69001kUttO9lqbhR15w","messageID":"msg_d87b60528001ED2R4yEIlGBbIN","sessionID":"ses_2784a0cd0ffegdT3ebJH7Cju7R","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_a18e7119a8504f849f53f54c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.md"},"output":"<path>/workspace/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>1: <!-- markdownlint-disable MD033 MD041 -->\n2: <p align=\"center\">\n3:   <a href=\"https://nonebot.dev/\"><img src=\"https://nonebot.dev/logo.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" alt=\"nonebot\"></a>\n4: </p>\n5: \n6: <div align=\"center\">\n7: \n8: # NoneBot\n9: \n10: <!-- prettier-ignore-start -->\n11: <!-- markdownlint-disable-next-line MD036 -->\n12: _✨ 跨平台 Python 异步机器人框架 ✨_\n13: <!-- prettier-ignore-end -->\n14: \n15: </div>\n16: \n17: <p align=\"center\">\n18:   <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nonebot/nonebot2/master/LICENSE\">\n19:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/nonebot/nonebot2\" alt=\"license\">\n20:   </a>\n21:   <a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/nonebot2\">\n22:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nonebot2?logo=python&logoColor=edb641\" alt=\"pypi\">\n23:   </a>\n24:   <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue?logo=python&logoColor=edb641\" alt=\"python\">\n25:   <a href=\"https://github.com/psf/black\">\n26:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-black-000000.svg?logo=python&logoColor=edb641\" alt=\"black\">\n27:   </a>\n28:   <a href=\"https://github.com/Microsoft/pyright\">\n29:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/types-pyright-797952.svg?logo=python&logoColor=edb641\" alt=\"pyright\">\n30:   </a>\n31:   <a href=\"https://github.com/astral-sh/ruff\">\n32:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/charliermarsh/ruff/main/assets/badge/v2.json\" alt=\"ruff\">\n33:   </a>\n34:   <br />\n35:   <a href=\"https://codecov.io/gh/nonebot/nonebot2\">\n36:     <img src=\"https://codecov.io/gh/nonebot/nonebot2/branch/master/graph/badge.svg?token=2P0G0VS7N4\" alt=\"codecov\"/>\n37:   </a>\n38:   <a href=\"https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/actions/workflows/website-deploy.yml\">\n39:     <img src=\"https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/actions/workflows/website-deploy.yml/badge.svg?branch=master&event=push\" alt=\"site\"/>\n40:   </a>\n41:   <a href=\"https://results.pre-commit.ci/latest/github/nonebot/nonebot2/master\">\n42:     <img src=\"https://results.pre-commit.ci/badge/github/nonebot/nonebot2/master.svg\" alt=\"pre-commit\" />\n43:   </a>\n44:   <a href=\"https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/actions/workflows/pyright.yml\">\n45:     <img src=\"https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/actions/workflows/pyright.yml/badge.svg?branch=master&event=push\" alt=\"pyright\">\n46:   </a>\n47:   <a href=\"https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/actions/workflows/ruff.yml\">\n48:     <img src=\"https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/actions/workflows/ruff.yml/badge.svg?branch=master&event=push\" alt=\"ruff\">\n49:   </a>\n50:   <br />\n51:   <a href=\"https://onebot.dev/\">\n52:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/OneBot-v11-black?style=social&logo=data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"onebot\">\n53:   </a>\n54:   <a href=\"https://onebot.dev/\">\n55:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/OneBot-v12-black?style=social&logo=data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"onebot\">\n56:   </a>\n57:   <a href=\"https://bot.q.qq.com/wiki/\">\n58:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/QQ-Bot-lightgrey?style=social&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,\" alt=\"QQ\">\n59:   </a>\n60:   <a href=\"https://core.telegram.org/bots/api\">\n61:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/telegram-Bot-lightgrey?style=social&logo=telegram\" alt=\"telegram\">\n62:   </a>\n63:   <a href=\"https://open.feishu.cn/document/home/index\">\n64:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6-Bot-lightgrey?style=social&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,\" alt=\"feishu\">\n65:   </a>\n66:   <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/developers/apps\">\n67:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-Bot-181717?style=social&logo=github\" alt=\"github\"/>\n68:   </a>\n69:   <!-- <a href=\"https://ding-doc.dingtalk.com/document#/org-dev-guide/elzz1p\">\n70:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/%E9%92%89%E9%92%89-Bot-lightgrey?style=social&logo=data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"dingtalk\"> -->\n71:   </a>\n72:   <br />\n73:   <a href=\"https://jq.qq.com/?_wv=1027&k=5OFifDh\">\n74:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/QQ%E7%BE%A4-768887710-orange?style=flat-square\" alt=\"QQ Chat Group\">\n75:   </a>\n76:   <a href=\"https://qun.qq.com/qqweb/qunpro/share?_wv=3&_wwv=128&appChannel=share&inviteCode=7b4a3&appChannel=share&businessType=9&from=246610&biz=ka\">\n77:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/QQ%E9%A2%91%E9%81%93-NoneBot-5492ff?style=flat-square\" alt=\"QQ Channel\">\n78:   </a>\n79:   <a href=\"https://t.me/botuniverse\">\n80:     <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/telegram-botuniverse-blue?style=flat-square\" alt=\"Telegram Channel\">\n81:   </a>\n82:   <a href=\"https://discord.gg/VKtE6Gdc4h\">\n83:     <img src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/847819937858584596/widget.png?style=shield\" alt=\"Discord Server\">\n84:   </a>\n85: </p>\n86: \n87: <p align=\"center\">\n88:   <a href=\"https://nonebot.dev/\">文档</a>\n89:   ·\n90:   <a href=\"https://nonebot.dev/docs/quick-start\">快速上手</a>\n91:   ·\n92:   <a href=\"#插件\">文档打不开？</a>\n93: </p>\n94: \n95: <p align=\"center\">\n96:   <a href=\"https://asciinema.org/a/569440\">\n97:     <img src=\"https://nonebot.dev/img/setup.svg\" alt=\"setup\" >\n98:   </a>\n99: </p>\n100: \n101: ## 简介\n102: \n103: NoneBot2 是一个现代、跨平台、可扩展的 Python 聊天机器人框架，它基于 Python 的类型注解和异步特性，能够为你的需求实现提供便捷灵活的支持。\n104: \n105: ## 特色\n106: \n107: - 异步优先：基于 Python 的异步特性，即使是~~非常~~大量的消息，也能吞吐自如\n108: - 易于开发：配合 NB-CLI 脚手架，代码编写上手简单，没有过多的冗余代码，可以让开发者专注于业务逻辑\n109: - 生而可靠：100% 类型注解覆盖，配合编辑器的类型推导功能，能将绝大多数的 Bug 杜绝在编辑器中 ([编辑器支持](https://nonebot.dev/docs/editor-support))\n110: - 社区丰富：社区用户众多，直接和间接用户超过十万人，每天都有大量的活跃用户 ([社区资源](#社区资源))\n111: - 海纳百川：一个框架，支持多个聊天软件平台，可自定义通信协议\n112: \n113:   |                                                       协议名称                                                        | 状态 |                                   注释                                    |\n114:   | :-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------: | :--: | :-----------------------------------------------------------------------: |\n115:   |               OneBot（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-onebot)，[协议](https://onebot.dev/)）                |  ✅  | 支持 QQ、TG、微信公众号、KOOK 等[平台](https://onebot.dev/ecosystem.html) |\n116:   |      Telegram（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-telegram)，[协议](https://core.telegram.org/bots/api)）      |  ✅  |                                                                           |\n117:   |     飞书（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-feishu)，[协议](https://open.feishu.cn/document/home/index)）     |  ✅  |                                                                           |\n118:   |         GitHub（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-github)，[协议](https://docs.github.com/en/apps)）          |  ✅  |                          GitHub APP & OAuth APP                           |\n119:   |                QQ（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-qq)，[协议](https://bot.q.qq.com/wiki/)）                |  ✅  |                            QQ 官方接口调整较多                            |\n120:   |                             Console（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-console)）                             |  ✅  |                                控制台交互                                 |\n121:   |     Red（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-red)，[协议](https://chrononeko.github.io/QQNTRedProtocol/)）      |  ✅  |                                 QQNT 协议                                  |\n122:   |           Satori（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-satori)，[协议](https://satori.js.org/zh-CN)）            |  ✅  |               支持 Onebot、TG、飞书、微信公众号、Koishi 等                |\n123:   |   Discord（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-discord)，[协议](https://discord.com/developers/docs/intro)）    |  ✅  |                             Discord Bot 协议                              |\n124:   |               DoDo（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-dodo)，[协议](https://open.imdodo.com/)）               |  ✅  |                               DoDo Bot 协议                               |\n125:   |        Kritor（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-kritor)，[协议](https://github.com/KarinJS/kritor)）         |  ✅  |                Kritor (OnebotX) 协议，QQNT 机器人接口标准                  |\n126:   |    Mirai（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-mirai)，[协议](https://docs.mirai.mamoe.net/mirai-api-http/)）    |  ✅  |                                  QQ 协议                                  |\n127:   |    Milky（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-milky)，[协议](https://milky.ntqqrev.org/)）                      |  ✅  |                           QQNT 机器人应用接口标准                          |\n128:   |         钉钉（[仓库](https://github.com/nonebot/adapter-ding)，[协议](https://open.dingtalk.com/document/)）          |  🤗  |                        寻找 Maintainer（暂不可用）                        |\n129:   |     开黑啦（[仓库](https://github.com/Tian-que/nonebot-adapter-kaiheila)，[协议](https://developer.kookapp.cn/)）     |  ↗️  |                                由社区贡献                                 |\n130:   |                          Ntchat（[仓库](https://github.com/JustUndertaker/adapter-ntchat)）                           |  ↗️  |                           微信协议，由社区贡献                            |\n131:   |                      MineCraft（[仓库](https://github.com/17TheWord/nonebot-adapter-minecraft)）                      |  ↗️  |                                由社区贡献                                 |\n132:   |                       Walle-Q（[仓库](https://github.com/onebot-walle/nonebot_adapter_walleq)）                       |  ↗️  |                            QQ 协议，由社区贡献                            |\n133:   |                       Villa（[仓库](https://github.com/CMHopeSunshine/nonebot-adapter-villa)）                        |  ❌  |                     米游社大别野 Bot 协议，官方已下线                     |\n134:   | Rocket.Chat（[仓库](https://github.com/IUnlimit/nonebot-adapter-rocketchat)，[协议](https://developer.rocket.chat/)） |  ↗️  |                     Rocket.Chat Bot 协议，由社区贡献                      |\n135:   |     Tailchat（[仓库](https://github.com/eya46/nonebot-adapter-tailchat)，[协议](https://tailchat.msgbyte.com/)）      |  ↗️  |                  Tailchat 开放平台 Bot 协议，由社区贡献                   |\n136:   |                             Mail（[仓库](https://github.com/mobyw/nonebot-adapter-mail)）                             |  ↗️  |                         邮件收发协议，由社区贡献                          |\n137:   |     黑盒语音（[仓库](https://github.com/lclbm/adapter-heybox)，[协议](https://github.com/QingFengOpen/HeychatDoc)）     |  ↗️  |                       黑盒语音机器人协议，由社区贡献                             |\n138:   | 微信公众平台（[仓库](https://github.com/YangRucheng/nonebot-adapter-wxmp)，[协议](https://developers.weixin.qq.com/doc/)）|  ↗️  |                       微信公众平台协议，由社区贡献                             |\n139:   | Gewechat（[仓库](https://github.com/Shine-Light/nonebot-adapter-gewechat)，[协议](https://github.com/Devo919/Gewechat)）|  ❌  |                      Gewechat 微信协议，Gewechat不再维护及可用                            |\n140:   |  EFChat（[仓库](https://github.com/molanp/nonebot_adapter_efchat)，[协议](https://irinu-live.melon.fish/efc-help/)）   |  ↗️  |                            恒五聊平台协议，由社区贡献                          |\n141:   |  VoceChat （[仓库](https://github.com/5656565566/nonebot-adapter-vocechat)，[协议](https://doc.voce.chat/zh-cn/bot/bot-and-webhook)）   |  ↗️  |                            VoceChat 平台协议，由社区贡献                          |\n142:   |  B站直播间（[仓库](https://github.com/MingxuanGame/nonebot-adapter-bilibili-live)，[Web API 协议](https://github.com/SocialSisterYi/bilibili-API-collect/blob/master/docs/live)，[开放平台协议](https://open-live.bilibili.com/document)）   |  ↗️  |                            B站直播间（Web API/开放平台）协议，由社区贡献                          |\n143: \n144: - 坚实后盾：支持多种 web 框架，可自定义替换、组合\n145: \n146:   |                              驱动框架                               |  类型  |\n147:   | :-----------------------------------------------------------------: | :----: |\n148:   |              [FastAPI](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/)               | 服务端 |\n149:   | [Quart](https://quart.palletsprojects.com/en/latest/)（异步 Flask） | 服务端 |\n150:   |           [aiohttp](https://docs.aiohttp.org/en/stable/)            | 客户端 |\n151:   |               [httpx](https://www.python-httpx.org/)                | 客户端 |\n152:   |     [websockets](https://websockets.readthedocs.io/en/stable/)      | 客户端 |\n153: \n154: 更多：[概览](https://nonebot.dev/docs/)\n155: \n156: ## 什么不是 NoneBot2\n157: \n158: NoneBot2 不是某个平台或者协议的具体实现，它只负责和已有协议适配器通信，并处理接收到的事件。所以，“NoneBot 有 blabla 平台的 blabla 功能吗？”这种问题是与 NoneBot2 无关的。请在相应平台的功能文档中确认，或与相应平台的协议适配开发者联系。\n159: \n160: NoneBot2 不是 NoneBot1 的替代品。事实上，它们都在被积极的维护着。但是，如果你想尝试一些新功能，或者想要支持更多的平台，可以考虑使用 NoneBot2。\n161: \n162: > ~~NoneBot2 和 NoneBot1 的区别，就像是 VisualStudio Code 和 VisualStudio 一样~~\n163: \n164: ## 即刻开始\n165: \n166: ~~完整~~文档可以在 [这里](https://nonebot.dev/) 查看。\n167: \n168: 懒得看文档？下面是快速安装指南：\n169: \n170: 1. 安装 [pipx](https://pypa.github.io/pipx/)\n171: \n172:    ```bash\n173:    python -m pip install --user pipx\n174:    python -m pipx ensurepath\n175:    ```\n176: \n177: 2. 安装脚手架\n178: \n179:    ```bash\n180:    pipx install nb-cli\n181:    ```\n182: \n183: 3. 使用脚手架创建项目\n184: \n185:    ```bash\n186:    nb create\n187:    ```\n188: \n189: 4. 运行项目\n190: \n191:    ```bash\n192:    nb run\n193:    ```\n194: \n195: ## 社区资源\n196: \n197: ### 常见问题\n198: \n199: - [常见问题解答(FAQ)](https://faq.nonebot.dev/)\n200: - [论坛(Discussion)](https://discussions.nonebot.dev/)\n201: \n202: ### 教程/实际项目/经验分享\n203: \n204: - [awesome-nonebot](https://github.com/nonebot/awesome-nonebot)\n205: \n206: ### 插件\n207: \n208: 此外，NoneBot2 还有丰富的官方以及第三方现成的插件供大家使用：\n209: \n210: - [NoneBot-Plugin-Docs](https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/tree/master/packages/nonebot-plugin-docs)：离线文档至本地项目使用 (别再说文档打不开了！)\n211: \n212:   在项目目录下执行：\n213: \n214:   ```bash\n215:   nb plugin install nonebot_plugin_docs\n216:   ```\n217: \n218:   或者尝试以下镜像：\n219: \n220:   - [文档镜像(中国境内)](https://nb2.baka.icu)\n221: \n222: - 其他插件请查看 [商店](https://nonebot.dev/store/plugins)\n223: \n224: ## 许可证\n225: \n226: `NoneBot` 采用 `MIT` 许可证进行开源\n227: \n228: ```text\n229: THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED \"AS IS\", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR\n230: IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO THE WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS\n231: FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE AND NONINFRINGEMENT. IN NO EVENT SHALL THE AUTHORS OR\n232: COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES OR OTHER LIABILITY, WHETHER\n233: IN AN ACTION OF CONTRACT, TORT OR OTHERWISE, ARISING FROM, OUT OF OR IN\n234: CONNECTION WITH THE SOFTWARE OR THE USE OR OTHER DEALINGS IN THE SOFTWARE.\n235: ```\n236: \n237: ## 贡献\n238: \n239: 请参考 [贡献指南](./CONTRIBUTING.md)\n240: \n241: ## 鸣谢\n242: \n243: ### 赞助者\n244: \n245: 感谢以下产品对 NoneBot 项目提供的赞助：\n246: \n247: <p align=\"center\">\n248:   <a href=\"https://github.com/\">\n249:     <picture>\n250:       <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/github-dark.png\">\n251:       <img src=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/github-light.png\" height=\"50\" alt=\"GitHub\">\n252:     </picture>\n253:   </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n254:   <a href=\"https://www.netlify.com/\">\n255:     <picture>\n256:       <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/netlify-dark.svg\">\n257:       <img src=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/netlify-light.svg\" height=\"50\" alt=\"netlify\">\n258:     </picture>\n259:   </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n260:   <a href=\"https://sentry.io/\">\n261:     <picture>\n262:       <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/sentry-dark.svg\">\n263:       <img src=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/sentry-light.svg\" height=\"50\" alt=\"sentry\">\n264:     </picture>\n265:   </a>\n266: </p>\n267: <p align=\"center\">\n268:   <a href=\"https://www.docker.com/\">\n269:     <picture>\n270:       <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/docker-dark.svg\">\n271:       <img src=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/docker-light.svg\" height=\"50\" alt=\"docker\">\n272:     </picture>\n273:   </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n274:   <a href=\"https://www.algolia.com/\">\n275:     <picture>\n276:       <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/algolia-dark.svg\">\n277:       <img src=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/algolia-light.svg\" height=\"50\" alt=\"algolia\">\n278:     </picture>\n279:   </a>\n280: </p>\n281: <p align=\"center\">\n282:   <a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/\">\n283:     <img src=\"https://resources.jetbrains.com/storage/products/company/brand/logos/jb_beam.svg\" height=\"80\" alt=\"JetBrains\" >\n284:   </a>\n285: </p>\n286: \n287: 感谢以下赞助者对 NoneBot 项目提供的资金支持：\n288: \n289: <a href=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/sponsors.svg\">\n290:   <img src=\"https://assets.nonebot.dev/sponsors.svg\" alt=\"sponsors\" />\n291: </a>\n292: \n293: ### 开发者\n294: \n295: 感谢以下开发者对 NoneBot2 作出的贡献：\n296: \n297: <a href=\"https://github.com/nonebot/nonebot2/graphs/contributors\">\n298:   <img src=\"https://contrib.rocks/image?repo=nonebot/nonebot2&max=1000\" alt=\"contributors\" />\n299: </a>\n\n(End of file - total 299 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<!-- markdownlint-disable MD033 MD041 -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n 